        <title>Unit Objectives for Instructors</title>
        <contents>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;By the end of this unit, you should be able to:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Articulate the reasons for integrating practice with critical thinking skills from the very beginning with adult ELLs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Create learning objectives that address critical thinking skills within any type of lesson&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Identify and practice ways (e.g., task type, questioning techniques, choice of content) to infuse these skills in your own classes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
